{"id": "1297950959636582472", "channel_id": "1297950959636582472", "type": 0, "author_id": "773037463626317887", "author_name": "fengtengjayden9754", "author_bot": false, "content": "相位对弈好像出Bug了，敌方回合因倒计时结束后，并没有轮到我的回合，而是卡在回合之间的环节。\n接着，我选择了投降，但我点击了十几次投降都没有效果，因此只好选择关闭游戏界面。", "timestamp": "2024-10-21T15:53:43.540000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-10-21T15:55:08.926000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1297950960290762753", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-10-21-23-15-14-27_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 172896, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1297950959636582472/1297950960290762753/Screenshot_2024-10-21-23-15-14-27_09a98f8d0fc2b11b1559c9fab3480a92.jpg?ex=69cbee07&is=69ca9c87&hm=dd7a813db4a7081ff38ca638b1aab301d11ac44b44693423c9fc8a1260944b96&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1297950959636582472", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "相位对弈的投降选项失效，还有在两个回合之间的环节卡死", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
